SETUP
------

Debian
-------
1. Install required packages
  sudo apt-get install build-essential ruby ruby-dev

2. Install required ruby gems
  sudo gem install rest-client pkg-wizard

RedHat
-------
1. Install required packages
  sudo yum install yum-utils ruby-devel gcc make automake ruby rubygems

2. Install required ruby gems
  sudo gem install rest-client pkg-wizard
